  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The rate of obesity and bariatric surgery is rising steadily. Though Bariatric Surgery
      Influences on aspects such as endocrin analysis, finance, etc are well tested, quantitative
      and quality voice impacts have not been evaluated. The aim of the study is to recruit 50
      patients who underwent bariatric surgery and compare voice quality in each of these patients
      before and after surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
